      <title>美国通胀小幅上升不会阻止美联储 9 月份降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/fed-rate-cuts-small-us-inflation-pickup-won-t-derail-a-september-move</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国通胀率七月份可能略有上升，但不足以阻止美联储下个月普遍预期的降息。]]></description>
